@model dynamic
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About the Work Log Management System";
}

<h2>@ViewBag.Title</h2>

<div>
    <p>
        The <strong>Work Log Management System</strong> is a web-based application designed to streamline and manage employee work logs effectively.
    </p>

    <p>
        This application is built using the ASP.NET MVC framework and leverages Entity Framework Core for database management with Microsoft SQL Server. 
        It enables administrators and employees to efficiently record, edit, and review work activities, ensuring that all work logs are accurately documented.
    </p>

    <h3>Key Features:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>User-friendly interface for managing work logs.</li>
        <li>Role-based access control to differentiate between administrators and employees.</li>
        <li>Comprehensive reporting and review functionality for work logs.</li>
        <li>Scalable and maintainable architecture following SOLID principles, YAGNI, and KISS methodologies.</li>
        <li>Integrated with ASP.NET Identity for secure authentication and authorization.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
        The system is designed to be scalable, maintainable, and easy to use, making it an ideal solution for organizations looking to improve their work log management processes.
    </p>
</div>

